<refnamediv><refname>imcomparehist</refname><refpurpose>Compare two histograms.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>value = imcomparehist(h1, h2, method)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para>Supported methods are <literal>correlation</literal>, <literal>chisqr</literal>, <literal>intersection</literal>, and <literal>bhattacharyya</literal>.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
[h, cells] = imcalchist(uint8([0 1; 1 2]), 3);
value = imcomparehist(h, h);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
